   <collaboration id="sid-8ee3d0d5-7e22-4d0e-a246-88e6bf2bc1fb">
      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="Track and monitor the completion of production order operations including: operation completion, tool release, actual vs. scheduled time capture, next operation identification, etc. All areas of production will perform operation completions at a level appropriate to facilitate high level of WIP traceability. Not all operations will require data entry. Some operations will be milestone operations where the system will relieve material through backflushing, and book labor in the system for all interim operations.  &#10;&#10;&#10;Examples of business requirements for production operation completion include: &#10;&#10;Ability to implement bar-coding technology. &#10;Ability to confirm operation completion 'real time.' &#10;Ability to provide WIP status and order progress &#10;Ability to capture and record actual time spent on each operation. &#10;Ability to automatically update tool usage records at operation completion. &#10;Ability to confirm completion by operation, order number, collective order, partially completed order. &#10;&#10;"/>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-approvedby" metaValue="[&quot;Shilpa Chandra&quot;]"/>
